     <a class="fn-clear" href="/article/105081.html" target="_blank" title="《暗黑复仇者2》：打铁还需自身硬"> <img class="fn-left" src="http://img.chuapp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/447_1416858729_247.png?imageView2/5/w/390/h/219" width="390" height="219" alt="" /> 
